{"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setSelected:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"selected","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":" if the view should display itself as selected; "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"if it should display itself as unselected."}]}],"name":"selected"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" if the change in selection state is animated; ","type":"text"},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" if the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"change is immediate.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"animated"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You should not call this method directly. A map view calls this method in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"response to user interactions with the annotation. Subclasses may override this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method in order to customize the appearance of the view depending on its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"selection state.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Related examples","anchor":"Related-examples","level":4},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/AnnotationViewExample","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/setSelected:animated:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"metadata":{"title":"setSelected:animated:","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L230"},"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(im)setSelected:animated:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setSelected:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setSelected:animated:","kind":"identifier"}]},"abstract":[{"text":"Sets the selection state of the annotation view with an optional animation.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/setselected:animated:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS/AnnotationViewExample":{"title":"Custom Annotation View","type":"topic","kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre-native-for-ios\/annotationviewexample","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/AnnotationViewExample","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Add a custom annotation view"}],"role":"article"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/setSelected:animated:":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setSelected:animated:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setSelected:animated:"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the selection state of the annotation view with an optional animation."}],"title":"setSelected:animated:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/setselected:animated:","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/setSelected:animated:"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"title":"MLNAnnotation","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationView"}],"title":"MLNAnnotationView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","type":"topic"}}}